data.description: Located in beautiful Sunrise, this waterfront house is a must see.  Low HOA fee and a great location. Beautiful lake view out the kitchen, lanai and master bedroom.  Large fenced backyard. Newer wood look tile floors throughout.  Vaulted ceilings in living/dining room, kitchen and master bedroom.  Spacious and open combination living/dining room allows flexibility with room use and furniture placement.  Kitchen with eat in breakfast area, granite countertops and wood cabinets with pantry. Newer stainless appliances. Spacious master bedroom with walk in closet.  Large screened lanai with attached sun shades for comfort while enjoying it. Accordion hurricane protection on all windows and sliding doors. Newer water heater.  Home price reflects updates and personalization that may be needed.
